Description: CLI toolkit for photo archive management
 Photos Manager CLI provides tools for finding duplicates, fixing timestamps,
 managing metadata, verifying integrity, and synchronizing photo archives.
 .
 Subcommands: find, prepare, locate, index, series, exifdates, fixdates,
 manifest, info, verify, sync.
